    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关键机制:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 资源采集：在 Forest Construction VR Demo 中，您可以获取几种基础的建筑材料来源，例如树木、石头和黏土。您可以使用各种工具进行采集，然后将收集到的材料切割成所需的部分，加工后用于建造。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/71d7bee4a221e2b9ddf9fb633df2e509.poster.avif?t=1759710333\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/71d7bee4a221e2b9ddf9fb633df2e509.webm?t=1759710333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/71d7bee4a221e2b9ddf9fb633df2e509.mp4?t=1759710333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 制作系统：在工作台上，采集到的资源可以被加工成各种建筑元素，例如砖块、木板、梁柱以及其他建筑部件。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/be7e55195623cabbceb244afcbd8c93b.poster.avif?t=1759710333\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/be7e55195623cabbceb244afcbd8c93b.webm?t=1759710333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/be7e55195623cabbceb244afcbd8c93b.mp4?t=1759710333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 建筑： 建筑机制允许您在任何角度和任何位置放置物体，使您能够建造各种各样的结构，如房屋、塔楼、桥梁，以及您能够想象到的任何东西，使用您收集和加工的材料。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/1f0394eed7d916916265ec20450c4bc7.poster.avif?t=1759710333\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/1f0394eed7d916916265ec20450c4bc7.webm?t=1759710333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/1f0394eed7d916916265ec20450c4bc7.mp4?t=1759710333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 互动性: Forest Construction VR Demo 提供了良好的物理互动体验。玩家需要搬运、运输、举起和握住工具和建筑材料，这些工具和材料具备了必要的物理特性，以实现真实的互动。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/af3169775954b99dee7dfec2d33b95e0.poster.avif?t=1759710333\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/af3169775954b99dee7dfec2d33b95e0.webm?t=1759710333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221550/extras/af3169775954b99dee7dfec2d33b95e0.mp4?t=1759710333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 无需生存的沙盒游戏：Forest Construction VR Demo 不局限于生存，而是邀请你沉浸在没有不必要限制的建设和实验创作过程中。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些关键机制将帮助您创建独特的建筑，享受建造过程，并沉浸在游戏的森林世界中舒适的氛围中。利用这些机会好好享受时光吧。</p>",
